INSTALLATION

In your home directory:

~ $ git clone git://github.com/jbe/.jconf.git
~ $ .jconf/install

Running .jconf/install adds a line to each *rc file, telling it to source the corresponding file in ~/.jconf/.


INCLUDED

.bashrc
.zshrc
.vimrc
.gvimrc
.screenrc
.irbrc
